Description: periscope2, like periscope, is targeting to build enterprise, scalable and UI-standardized 'shiny' applications 
    but with bootstrap v4 features and with more helpful shiny modules and enhanced application files organization aiming to both 
    building powerful application development and enriching shiny developers experience for building and maintaining applications.  
